Edgar Academy Padel Tournament. 

3 courts, 6 teams, 1:30 h play. 10 mins play, then who wins moves 1 court up, shuffling the pairs around. Prize: the winner doesn't have to show up to the next match. So that we all have a chance to win next time ('cause they're too good for us). 

Last 30mins spent playing Around The World on the Central Court. 6 people on one side, 6 people getting tanned on the other. 

Next time: we do this while drunk.
